        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-12-01T03:22:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Then again, it looks like traditional headers provide this too. For example, I see it in android-ndk-r15c/platforms/android-16/arch-x86/usr/include/linux/elf.h.",
      "revId": "83c3acca564849bab1705b4b2d39c9c6f53baeb9",
